name: "el estail de zorzal"
description:
"tropical boom bap" is a collection based on portraits of argentinian and other latin american artists with 3a5a1a style. 20 eds each artwork.
"el estail del zorzal"shows us the uruguayan? argentinean? french? whatever, the legend of tango Carlos Gardel, standing very well in front of the camera by Gucci, wearing his custom hat matching straps and a beautiful shirt, lots of style and lots of bling bling on the necklace, on the ring and on his tooth. 
to complement, some beautiful face tats.
splendid outfit carlos, es por ahí.
